name: Vibrant Grotesque Horror
description:
This model is a merge of my Erotic Grotesque Horror model and Colorjizz and You can create surreal, vibrant horror images with it. Using the trigger word isn't needed to get horror, of course, but if you want it really colorful, use it.

using higher steps is often better.

The last two sample images did not use the trigger word.

I use vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned but it's not a requirement.
